This paper is about hyperparameter optimization in deep learning, which is a topic that spans multiple sub-fields of computer science. However, given the focus on deep learning models and their optimization, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
